        "html": "<style>.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a0f1a 0%,#0f1535 40%,#1a103a 100%);position:relative;overflow:hidden;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff}.accent-line{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#6366f1,#818cf8,#a5b4fc)}.cover-content{display:flex;height:100%;padding:60px}.cover-left{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding-right:20px}.cover-right{width:300px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center}.cover-right img{height:480px;width:auto;object-fit:contain;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.5))}.category-badge{display:inline-block;background:rgba(99,102,241,.2);border:1px solid #6366f1;color:#818cf8;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:20px;width:fit-content}.cover-title{font-size:46px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:16px}.cover-title .hl{color:#818cf8}.cover-sub{font-size:22px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:20px}.cover-badges{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}.cover-badges span{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding:6px 14px;border-radius:16px;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.cover-author{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:60px;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}.cover-copy{position:absolute;bottom:20px;right:60px;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}</style><div class='slide'><div class='accent-line'></div><div class='cover-content'><div class='cover-left'><div class='category-badge'>医師×AI実験記録</div><div class='cover-title'>医師が<span class='hl'>Claude Code</span>で<br>医療アプリを<br>作ってみた</div><div class='cover-sub'>プログラミング未経験 → アプリ3本リリース</div><div class='cover-badges'><span>InsuCalc</span><span>DM Compass</span><span>T1Life</span></div></div><div class='cover-right'><img src='https://sns-hub-five.vercel.app/dr-iwatatsu.png' alt='Dr.いわたつ'></div></div><div class='cover-author'>Dr.いわたつ / 糖尿病専門医・指導医</div><div class='