        "html": "<style>.slide-apps{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a0f1a,#0f1535);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;padding:50px;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:28px}.badge{background:rgba(99,102,241,.2);color:#818cf8;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.logo{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}.slide-title{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}.app-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}.app-row{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,.25);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px}.app-icon{font-size:44px;flex-shrink:0}.app-info{flex:1}.app-name{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:#818cf8;margin-bottom:4px}.app-desc{font-size:22px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.app-tags{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:8px}.app-tag{background:rgba(99,102,241,.12);color:#a5b4fc;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:12px;font-size:18px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:50px;right:50px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}</style><div class='slide-apps'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>📱 開発実績</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='slide-title'>作ったアプリ3本</div><div class='app-list'><div class='app-row'><div class='app-icon'>💉</div><div class='app-info'><div class='app-name'>InsuCalc</div><div class='app-desc'>インスリン量計算ツール。ガイドラインに基づく補正計算を一瞬で</div><div class='app-tags'><span class='app-tag'>医師向け</span><span class='app-tag'>病棟で使用中</span></div></div></div><div class='app-row'><div class='app-icon'>🧭</div><div class='app-info'><div class='app-name'>DM Compass</div><div class='app-desc'>糖尿病病棟オールインワン。低血糖対応・周術期管理・血糖目標設定</div><div class='app-tags'><span class='app-tag'>研修医向け</span><span class='app-tag'>医師向け</span></div></div></div><div class='app-row'><div class='app-icon'>📱</div><div class='app-info'><div class='app-name'>T1Life</div><div class='app-desc'>1型糖尿病患者向け。毎日の自己管理をサポートするツール</div><div class='app-tags'><span class='app-tag'>患者向け</span><span class='app-tag'>1型糖尿病</span></div></div></div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
