        "html": "<style>.slide-flow{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a0f1a,#0f1535);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;padding:50px;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:28px}.badge{background:rgba(99,102,241,.2);color:#818cf8;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.logo{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}.slide-title{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}.flow-steps{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:28px}.flow-box{background:rgba(99,102,241,.08);border:2px solid rgba(99,102,241,.25);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;flex:1}.flow-num{font-size:28px;font-weight:900;color:#818cf8;margin-bottom:6px}.flow-text{font-size:22px;color:#fff;line-height:1.4}.flow-arrow{font-size:32px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}.terminal-box{background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);border:1px solid rgba(99,102,241,.3);border-radius:12px;padding:24px;font-family:monospace}.term-prompt{color:#a5f3a0;font-size:22px}.term-cmd{color:#fff;font-size:22px}.term-comment{color:rgba(99,102,241,.7);font-size:20px;margin-top:6px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:50px;right:50px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}</style><div class='slide-flow'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>⚙ 開発プロセス</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='slide-title'>コードを書かずに医療アプリを作る方法</div><div class='flow-steps'><div class='flow-box'><div class='flow-num'>1</div><div class='flow-text'>現場の課題を<br>言語化する</div></div><div class='flow-arrow'>→</div><div class='flow-box'><div class='flow-num'>2</div><div class='flow-text'>Claude Codeに<br>日本語で伝える</div></div><div class='flow-arrow'>→</div><div class='flow-box'><div class='flow-num'>3</div><div class='flow-text'>フィードバックを<br>繰り返す</div></div><div class='flow-arrow'>→</div><div class='flow-box'><div class='flow-num'>4</div><div class='flow-text'>Vercelで<br>デプロイ</div></div></div><div class='terminal-box'><div class='term-prompt'>$ claude-code</div><div class='term-cmd'>> インスリン補正計算ツールを作って。患者の血糖値と目標値を入力したら<br>> 補正量が出るようにして</div><div class='term-comment'>// → コードが自動生成される</div></div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
