        "html": "<style>.slide-skill{width:1280px;height:720px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1b4b,#3730a3,#4338ca);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;color:#fff;padding:50px;position:relative}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:36px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);color:#fff;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.logo{font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}.slide-title{font-size:38px;font-weight:900;text-align:center;margin-bottom:36px}.vs-wrap{display:flex;gap:30px;align-items:center}.vs-col{flex:1;border-radius:20px;padding:30px;text-align:center}.vs-col.before{background:rgba(239,68,68,.15);border:2px solid rgba(239,68,68,.3)}.vs-col.after{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25)}.vs-label{font-size:24px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:12px}.vs-text{font-size:34px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.4}.vs-col.before .vs-text{color:#f87171}.vs-col.after .vs-text{color:#fff}.vs-divider{text-align:center;font-size:52px;flex-shrink:0;color:rgba(255,255,255,.4)}.bottom-msg{text-align:center;margin-top:28px;font-size:30px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.5;padding:20px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:16px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:50px;right:50px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5)}</style><div class='slide-skill'><div class='header'><span class='badge'>💡 AI時代のスキル</span><span class='logo'>Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class='slide-title'>医師に本当に必要なスキルとは</div><div class='vs-wrap'><div class='vs-col before'><div class='vs-label'>必要でないもの</div><div class='vs-text'>コーディング<br>スキル</div></div><div class='vs-divider'>→</div><div class='vs-col after'><div class='vs-label'>本当に必要なもの</div><div class='vs-text'>課題設定力<br>（何を作るか<br>を言語化）</div></div></div><div class='bottom-msg'>プログラミングは「書けない」でも「作れる」<br>これがAI時代の本質</div><div class='footer'><span>© Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
